high_descs: Turn right, and look down at the bin to the right of the sink.
Pick up the toilet paper from the bin.
Turn around and walk to the shelves.
Put the toilet paper down on the second shelf.
Turn around and walk to the white dresser.
Pick up the tube from the white dresser.
Turn around and walk to the white shelves.
Put the tube down on the second shelf to the left of the toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: To move toilet paper and a tube to the shelf.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the trash can that is sitting on the floor to the right of the sink
Pick up the roll of toilet paper that is sitting in the trash can
Turn around and face the long white counter with the shelves underneath
Place the toilet paper on the top shelf underneath in front of the candle stick
Turn left and walk to the door, then turn left and walk to the tall stand with the drawers
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll that is sitting on top of the stand
Turn around and walk to the long counter with the shelves underneath
Place the empty toilet paper roll on the shelf to the left of the roll of toilet paper
anns.task_desc: Place a new and an empty toilet paper roll on a shelf

high_descs: Turn right and go to the gray trash can on the floor across the bathroom.
Pick up the new toilet paper in the trash can.
Turn around and go to the white shelves across the bathroom.
Place the new toilet paper on the middle shelf.
Turn around and go to the dresser on the right.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll from the top of the dresser.
Turn around and go back to the white shelves.
Place the empty toilet paper roll on the left of the new toilet paper.
anns.task_desc: Move the toilet paper rolls to the shelves.
